{{Quote|Don't forget, Raquoran, this New Republic has some queer ideas about alien rights. They believe the Velcar Free Commerce Zone exists only to exploit defenseless aliens. I'll wager they can't wait to hatch some liberation plot for the Entymals that work the gas mines around Bextar. Gas mines that my Amber Sun Industries run &mdash; and are supposedly under your protection.|Elta Besk during the [[Pentastar Talks]]|<ref name="PA" />}}
'''Amber Sun Mining Corporate''', also known as '''Amber Sun Industries''', was a gas-[[Mining/Legends|mining]] subsidiary of [[Dynamic Automata]]. Their operations included gas-mining in the [[Bextar system/Legends|Bextar system]] which was known for its use of exploited alien labor during the reign of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] and the [[Pentastar Alignment]].

